<codeline><highlight class="normal">The<sp/>main<sp/>menu<sp/>works<sp/>with<sp/>a<sp/>KEYBOARD<sp/>only<sp/>and<sp/>up/down<sp/>arrow<sp/>keys<sp/>are<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>navigate<sp/>the<sp/>menu.<sp/>You<sp/>can<sp/>enter<sp/>the<sp/>IP<sp/>address<sp/>directly<sp/>by<sp/>typing<sp/>using<sp/>the<sp/>keyboard.</highlight></codeline>
