<codeline><highlight class="normal">IMPORTANT:<sp/>It<sp/>is<sp/>important<sp/>to<sp/>note<sp/>that<sp/>before<sp/>the<sp/>PROMOTION<sp/>move,<sp/>you<sp/>will<sp/>have<sp/>to<sp/>press<sp/>q(queen),<sp/>r(rook),<sp/>k(knight),<sp/>or<sp/>b(bishop)<sp/>on<sp/>the<sp/>keyboard<sp/>before<sp/>making<sp/>hitting<sp/>the<sp/>right<sp/>mouse<sp/>button.<sp/>By<sp/>default,<sp/>the<sp/>game<sp/>promotes<sp/>all<sp/>pawns<sp/>to<sp/>Queen.</highlight></codeline>
